data.description: The best way to describe this charming property is modern farmhouse in the mountains! The owners have poured so much care into every detail and it shows in every room. You get plenty of Privacy surrounded by woods, yet you're just a few minutes off of the spur in Gatlinburg. So many new things in this home, new tile backsplash, appliances, all new lights , switches, and plugs. New HVAC with UV light filtration, whole home water filter, portable generator, Trex decking on the back porch (with a hot tub!!) that has been completely screened in, the PERFECT front porch, a charming bathroom remodel, new insulation , an attached garage plus detached carport with lots of extra parking, and so much more! Huge windows to let in light all throughout the first floor, a walk-in closet ready for you to fill, soaring ceilings and the stunning gas fireplace Are just a few of the features that will make this feel like your perfect mountain home. Norton Creek is a highly sought after permanent residence or private vacation home community. Are you ready to move to the mountains?
